Package: scdown
Type: Package
Title: Simple Downstream Analysis After Cell Annotation
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Daiki",
      family = "User",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "daik54015@gmail.com"
    )
  )
Description: Provides a simple, practical downstream workflow for annotated
    single-cell RNA-seq data with an emphasis on immune-focused datasets.
    The package keeps the interface short while separating lightweight
    exploration from sample-aware testing. Inputs are standardized into a
    sparse-first matrix representation, then reused across maps, markers,
    user-selected genes, composition, annotation quality, signatures,
    communication, and compact HTML reports.
